## Template: Rate_Card_Counter
**Used for:** [COUNTER-OFFER] — Budget too low or unstated

Hi [Sender Name],

Thank you for thinking of Simplify to Glorify. We are honored.

For paid partnerships, our current sponsorship baseline is $300. For product exchange collaborations, we look for creators whose audience is actively engaged in faith, wellness, or intentional living (typically 5k+ followers or 3k+ email subscribers with demonstrated engagement).

If there is flexibility in the budget or if you would like to share your media kit and audience insights, we would be happy to revisit. We also have an affiliate program if a commission structure works better for your model.

Best,
[Founder Name]
Simplify to Glorify

